				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Novice Andrick, a junior member of the cult of the Absolute, has been sent by his supposed superior to attack an owlbear - a wild creature that killed another cultist. He needs to be be emboldened to attack the beast with a small pep talk. If the player does something to arouse suspicion however, Andrick may realise he's been tricked and turn hostile."
